Author: RealityClash
Title: Reality Clash - Turns Game into Reality - Bounty Promotion Program
Body: I don't believe that I ever said 'months', we're talking days, not months.  It is simple: Token Market has to send each bounty payment manually. There are a lot of bounty participants and therefore the process of manually checking and then sending RCC takes time.  There is no reason for anyone to be angry. I have explained the error - we announced that the bounty was being paid on twitter, but we hadn't been told that Token Market needed to do final checks before distributing. Now we know that Token Market also need to distribute RCC manually, we can accept that this takes some time. If bounty hunters are desperate for the RCC so that they can sell it immediately, then that is fine, but patience is a necessity. It would be far wiser for bounty participants to hold their RCC until game launch as this would likely result in highest return. But we do not dictate what happens on the marketplaces, if bounty participants want to sell their RCC immediately at a lower price, go ahead.  Thanks for your patience with Token Market.

Author: RealityClash
Title: Reality Clash - Turns Game into Reality - Bounty Promotion Program
Body: It is not about controlling the price or stopping people from selling RCC. It is the process that Token Market undertakes before distributing bounty. If we were in control of bounty distribution, it would have taken place but I cannot speak for Token Market - who I'm sure are incredibly busy and are dealing with distribution as fast as they possibly can.

Author: RealityClash
Title: Reality Clash - Turns Game into Reality - Bounty Promotion Program
Body: Reality Clash had their token sale managed by Token Market. The bounty program fell under the jurisdiction of Token Market. The bounty manager was sourced by Token Market. The bounty manager collected stake information, calculated bounty amounts and sent this to Token Market already. Token Market are manually distributing the bounty RCC. Each address is entered from spreadsheet and then amount is checked and sent to that address. This is a slow process as there are over 1000 addresses to send to.  I am suggesting that if you want a direct answer from the people handling the bounty distribution, you can just email support@tokenmarket.net  I didn't say I am angry... I don't understand why you think this?  Realistically, it has not been very long to wait at all. Irfan sent the stakes information to Token Market and they will distribute your bounties. It is my job to assist the community and support you guys at all times. But i have given the same answer so many times and nobody seems to be reading what I am saying.... so I am providing the email of the company doing the distribution, so you may get a direct answer.   I hope this clarifies matters.

Author: RealityClash
Title: Reality Clash - Turns Game into Reality - Bounty Promotion Program
Body: Win a one-of-a-kind personalized weapon for use in the game: https://reality-clash.com/win-your-own-gun/  Reality Clash, the world‚Äôs first Augmented Reality (AR) mobile combat game, is running a competition to win a personalized machine gun, open to all participants of its ongoing token sale.  The innovative FPS (First Person Shooter) game uses the camera on the player‚Äôs iOS or Android mobile device to overlay graphics onto their real-world environment, so that streets, buildings and other features become part of the game‚Äôs landscape. Now, Reality Clash are offering the chance to token sale contributors to get their name in the game through a personalised gun to use in combat. The gun has been designed exclusively for the Reality Clash referral competition and will be the only style gun ever made for the game.  How to enter Anyone who participates in the crowdsale will receive an email containing a referral code and link. All deposits that take place via a referral link will earn that referrer a 5% bonus in RCC Gold, the in-game currency. RCC Gold gives players access to inventory such as weapons, armour and other equipment.  The winner of the competition will be the person who accrues the largest referral balance by the end of the crowdsale, at 5pm UTC on 29 September 2017. To take part simply sign up and deposit any amount of Ether (ETH) to the Reality Clash token sale, and receive your referral link for promotional use.  $2M pledged to date Over $2 million was raised in the Reality Clash pre-sale. Participants in the current crowd sale will be able to purchase RCC Gold coins at a 70% discount now and then get exclusive access to weapons from November 2017. Crowdsale participants will have access to unique weaponry that will not be issued again afterwards, and will be eligible for an early demo of the game.  For any questions regarding the referral program contact support@tokenmarket.net. To participate in the crowdsale visit https://reality-clash.com  Those who have already participated in the token sale will automatically receive an email with referral details. Pre-sale participants please email info@reality-clash.com directly for your referral code. The winner will be announced one week after the token sale closes, and referral bonuses will be credited in RCC Gold after the end of the sale.  Good luck!  P.S. Remember: All project discussion or non-bounty related questions should be posted here: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2036661.0

Author: SergV
Title: Reality Clash - Turns Game into Reality - Bounty Promotion Program
Body: Hi irfan_pak10. I have more than once described the unpleasant situation surrounding my participation in Twitter and the Facebook campaign. It is not resolved, so I have to stop participating in it. On August 6, I signed up for the campaign, but accidentally incorrectly filled out the Bitcointalk Profile Link (No. 858 in the Spreadsheet of the Twitter Campaign, No. 691 in the Spreadsheet of Facebook). I registered again (Twitter No. 922, No.  719 Facebook) and asked the manager in private message (August 08, 2017) to delete incorrect entries. But the situation remained unchanged. I am again appealing to the forum manager (post No.  76 https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2036661.msg20812249#msg20812249). Later I noticed that my status in the spreadsheet has changed to Rejected. I tried to find out why this happened on the forum (post No.  487 https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=2028934.msg21337912#msg21337912). Author: jamalaezaz
Title: Reality Clash - Turns Game into Reality - Bounty Promotion Program
Body: Update#1: The Rejection due to Low quality, does not mean its permanent. There will be a second round of post count and revision at the end of crowdsale, And where we'll see if you have made more than 60% posts in English boards we'll will accept you.  Update#2: Our Spreadsheets are copied from the original spreadsheets, so we have to update the entries manually once a day or within 48 hours. So please always wait for it before posting here.        ANN [RCC] Reality Clash - First ARG Mobile Game with ERC-20 Armory   BOUNTY CAMPAIGN SPECIFICS  For this bitcointalk bounty program, Reality Clash has reserved 1,000,000 of Total Sold Coin During ICO Crowdsale. All of these RCC tokens will be fully distributed among the Reality Clash bounty campaign participants. As the total amount of participants is unknown, the RCC token will be allocated, based on a predetermined amount for each bounty campaign.  We are looking forward to engaging with you!  Distribution of Rewards  Social Media campaign: 20% Blog/Media Campaign: 20% Translation Campaign: 15% Signature Campaign: 30% Slack/Telegram Campaign: 5% Other Bounties: 10%  Note: Bounties will be distributed at the end of crowd sale.  Most Important: Once an ETH address is submitted, it will not be changed for any reason. Be careful when submitting your ETH address. Do not submit ETH addresses from an exchange ShapeShift, mixers, or any other 3rd party service. Provide only ETH addresses to which you know your private keys (or seed phrases).  Below you will find a detailed list of different bounty campaigns.     20% of the total Bounty Pool will be allocated for Social Media Campaign bounties which will be divided equally Between Facebook and Twitter Bounties.   Payments   5 Stakes per Week for Every Valid Twitter and Facebook User.   How to Join   For Twitter Follow the Official Twitter Handle here  Fill the form to Join  For Facebook   Like Official Facebook Fanpage here  Fill the form to Join  Terms and Rules  1: Twitter Accounts must have a Minimum of 200 Followers. and Facebook accounts must have a minimum of 100 Friends. 2: Twitter/Facebook accounts must be original. Fake, dead, inactive and bot accounts will not be accepted. 3: You must be an active and regular twitter user, and must be retweeting/sharing RalityClash's official tweets and updates. 4: Joining with multiple accounts is not allowed. Users found to be using multi accounts, will be blacklisted. 5: A user can participate in both campaigns at the same time. 5: Terms and Condition can be changed or more can be applied.  Accepted Participant List     Description Write a quality blog post, review the project, or create a quality video presentation and earn Reality Clash tokens as a part of our Blog and Media Program. All blogs and media content will be divided into 3 different categories, and will be rewarded as follows:   Payment Good: 100 Stakes Medium: 70 Stakes Normal: 40 Stakes   All content will be judged on the basis of quality, traffic, views and influence.   Terms and Conditions 1. Low-quality articles and videos will not be accepted. 2. Article and videos must be genuine. Copying graphics, text and other content are not allowed. (You can use official images, logos, graphics posted on the website, ANN thread, Facebook, and Twitter) 3. Articles must be longer than 500 characters, fewer than 500 characters will not be accepted. 4. Video must be at least 1:30 minutes long, shorter videos will not be accepted. 5. Article must have a link to the official website: (link)  and a link to the whitepaper: (whitepaper link) 7. Medium, Steemit, Newbium, and other general/free blogging platforms are allowed but only one post will be accepted on those platforms per user. 8. 3 blog posts/articles will be accepted in .com .net .org and other premium websites and blogs. 9. To proof your ownership of the blog or media you must add your bitcointalk profile link to your blog posts footer, and for video creators, your Bitcointalk profile must be added in in video description. 10. Manager and owners save the rights to increase or change any rules, payment structure and anything else if necessary.  Join here  Accepted Participant List    Earn RealityClash Tokens as Reward By Translating RealityClash Project‚Äôs Whitepaper, Announcement Thread and Moderating and Managing the thread. Keeping that active by Posting regular updates, news announcements from official thread, facebook and twitter.   Payment 15% of total Bounty Pool will be Paid to Translations and Moderations/Managements.  Whitepaper: 300 Stakes ANN thread+Bounty Thread: 150 Stakes Moderation/Management: 5 Stakes per Valid Post.  Translation Terms and Conditions  1: Translations must be original, using any kind of tools such as Google are not allowed. If found the translator will be blacklisted. 2: ANN thread translator will be responsible for the moderation as well (we have additional rewards for moderation). The translator must keep the thread active by translation of official announcements, news, posts. 3: We do not need any Signel Post Dead Thread. If you failed to keep the thread active and up to date, your reward can be reduced to 50% of the actual payment or you could simply be disqualified. 4: Increasing the moderation post count by spam posts, posting false posts or paying other to ask questions in your thread is not allowed. 5: Newbies i.e. users with no previous experience of translation will not be accepted.
